channel.title: If you need help portforwarding read here !!
channel.description: Ok everyone this is for everyone who needs help portforwarding, I myself was in this situation, than i googled a few things and found this site, that has ALL THE GUIDES you need to help you portforward and if you still dont get it, just post something on that site and they will help you ASAP, and they also give you a program that allows you to portforward as if you reading a book?? This really works so if you need help portforwarding read this and check this site out, it'll answer all your questions and help you with all your needs! The site is http://forums.pcwintech.com/ and be sure to register, than scroll down to "portforwarding" and be specific, they deal with all types of portforwarding not just for RSPS, Thank you all and hopefully this helps all you guys out! because it sure did for me! Sincerly, Trublue
